    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty in person! It is in absolutely stunning shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, always keeping it tucked away in the garage and staying on top of every little detail. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for its next adventure, this is the one. It\u2019s super clean, runs like a dream, and I\u2019d love to see it go to a great home. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 44900.0,
