    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. Featuring a high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, the valvetrain is whisper-quiet following a recent shim adjustment. The VANOS system has been fully overhauled with Beisan components, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced for structural longevity. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension features refreshed bushings and Bilstein PSS10 dampers for precise turn-in and exceptional lateral stability. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with zero oxidation or rock chips. A truly concours-ready driver\u2019s car with documented service history.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Full service records. No accidents. Smoke-free interior. Professionally detailed.",
