    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a rare find for the discerning collector or enthusiast. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, protected by a professional ceramic coating and completely free of chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, and the dashboard is pristine with every electronic component functioning exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively garage-kept and serviced ahead of schedule at authorized centers. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, every detail reflects a life of meticulous care. This is not just a used car; it is a preserved piece of automotive excellence, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
